401204329/https://www.moh.gov.gr/articles/ministry/grafeio-typoy/press-releases/6985-enhmerwsh-diapisteymenwn-syntaktwn-ygeias-apo-ton-yfypoyrgo-politikhs-prostasias-kai-diaxeirishs-krisewn-niko-xardalia-kai-ton-ekproswpo-toy-ypoyrgeioy-ygeias-gia-to-neo-koronoio-kathhghth-swthrh-tsiodra-30-3-2020|archive-date=1 April 2020|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|ISL}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Iceland|Iceland]]\n|1,562\n|6\n|460\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.covid.is/data |title=covid.is/data |last=Ss |date=2 April 2020 |website=Mbl |language=En |access-date=3 April 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200403102907/https://www.covid.is/data |archive-date=3 April 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|UKR}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Ukraine|Ukraine]]\n|1,319\n|38\n|28\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://moz.gov.ua/article/news/moz-povidomljae-pro-dva-novih-pidtverdzhenih-vipadki-koronavirusu-v-ukraini |title=\u041c\u041e\u0417 \u043f\u043e\u0432\u0456\u0434\u043e\u043c\u043b\u044f\u0454 \u043f\u0440\u043e \u0434\u0432\u0430 \u043d\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0445 \u043f\u0456\u0434\u0442\u0432\u0435\u0440\u0434\u0436\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0445 \u0432\u0438\u043f\u0430\u0434\u043a\u0438 \u043a\u043e\u0440\u043e\u043d\u0430\u0432\u0456\u0440\u0443\u0441\u0443 \u0432 \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0457\u043d\u0456 |access-date=14 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200319091128/https://moz.gov.ua/article/news/moz-povidomljae-pro-dva-novih-pidtverdzhenih-vipadki-koronavirusu-v-ukraini |archive-date=19 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|CRO}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Croatia|Croatia]]\n|1,222\n|16\n|130\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.koronavirus.hr/en |title=Official government website for accurate and verified information on Coronavirus |publisher=Government of the Republic of Croatia |language=English |access-date=27 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326135722/https://www.koronavi