ert Alberts]]\n|-\n| Assistant Coach ||  {{Flagicon|IDN}} [[Budiman Yunus]]\n|-\n| Goalkeeping Coach || {{Flagicon|BRA}} [[:id:Luizinho passos|Luizinho passos]]\n|-\n| Fitness Coach || {{Flagicon|IDN}} [[:id:Yaya Sunarya|Yaya Sunarya]]\n|-\n| Doctor || {{Flagicon|IDN}} [[:id:Mohammad Raffi Ghani|Mohammad Raffi Ghani]] \n|-\n| Physioterapist || {{Flagicon|IDN}} [[:id:Benidektus Adi Prianto|Benidektus Adi Prianto]] \n|-\n| General Secretary || {{Flagicon|IDN}} Yudiana\n|}\n\n=== Head Coach history ===\n''Head Coach by years (1982\u2013present)''\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!style=\"background:Blue; color:white;\"|Name\n!style=\"background:Blue; color:white;\"|From\n!style=\"background:Blue; color:white;\"|To\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Omo Suratmo\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1982\n| align=center| 1983\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Ade Dana\n| align=center| 1984\n| align=center| 1985\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Nandar Iskandar\n| align=center| 1985\n| align=center|1986\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Ade Dana\n| align=center| 1989\n| align=center| 1990\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Indra Thohir\n| align=center| 1993\n| align=center| 1995\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Risnandar Soendoro\n| align=center| 1995\n| align=center| 1996\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} M. Suryamin\n| align=center| 1998\n| align=center| 2000\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Indra Thohir\n| align=center| 2000\n| align=center| 2000\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Deny Syamsudin\n| align=center| 2001\n| align=center| 2002\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Poland}} Marek Andrzej \u015aledzianowski\n| align=center| 2003\n| align=center| 2003\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Chile}} Juan Antonio P\u00e1ez\n| align=center| 2003\n| align=center| 2005\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Indra Thohir\n| align=center| 2005\n| align=center| 2006\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Risnandar Soendoro\n| align=center| 2006\n| align=center| 2006\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Moldova}} {{flagicon|Indonesia}}[[Arcan Iurie]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2006\n