enig\n | first=Stuart\n | title=The Twisted Tale of Glam Rock\n | publisher=[[Praeger Publishers|Praeger]]\n | year=2010\n | isbn=978-0313379864\n | ref = harv\n}}\n*{{cite book\n | last = Metz\n | first = Allen\n | first2 = Carol\n | last2 = Benson\n | title = The Madonna Companion: Two Decades of Commentary\n | publisher = [[Music Sales Group]]\n | year = 1999\n | isbn = 0-8256-7194-9\n | ref = harv\n }}\n*{{cite book\n | last = Ryan\n | first = Gavin\n | title = Australia's Music Charts 1988-2010\n | year = 2011\n | publisher = Moonlight Publishing\n | location = Mt. Martha, VIC, Australia\n | ref = harv\n }}\n*{{cite book\n | last = Taraborrelli\n | first = Randy J.\n | authorlink = J. Randy Taraborrelli\n | title = [[Madonna: An Intimate Biography]]\n | publisher = [[Simon & Schuster]]\n | year = 2008\n | isbn = 9780330454469\n | ref = harv\n }}\n{{refend}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{YouTube|WyhdvRWEWRw|\"Erotica\" (music video)}}\n\n{{Madonna songs}}\n\n[[Category:1992 singles]]\n[[Category:1992 songs]]\n[[Category:Billboard Dance Club Songs number-one singles]]\n[[Category:European Hot 100 Singles number-one singles]]\n[[Category:Madonna (entertainer) songs]]\n[[Category:Maverick Records singles]]\n[[Category:New jack swing songs]]\n[[Category:Number-one singles in Greece]]\n[[Category:Number-one singles in Italy]]\n[[Category:Sire Records singles]]\n[[Category:Songs about BDSM]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Madonna (entertainer)]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Shep Pettibone]]\n[[Category:Song recordings produced by Madonna (entertainer)]]\n[[Category:Song recordings produced by Shep Pettibone]]\n[[Category:Trip hop songs]]\n[[Category:Warner Records singles]]\n[[Category:Songs involved in plagiarism controversies]]\n", "name_user": "John of Reading", "label": "safe", "comment": "Typo/generalfixes, replaced: on 2012 \u2192 in 2012", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erotica_(song)"}
